      <h1 class="sw-title">Candles on the Altar</h1>
      <p class="sw-sub">
        The perpetual fire of Vesta, the fire altars of Zoroaster, and why the modern church's candles are not Biblical
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- ── MODE BAR ── -->
    <div class="sw-mode-bar">
